---
// Section 5 — The debrief (the unique payoff). The ONE sanctioned bordered
// block (it IS the artifact, not decoration). survived/failed data colors are
// only sanctioned here.
---

<section aria-labelledby="debrief-title" class="border-t border-hairline">
  <div class="mx-0 max-w-[720px] px-6 py-16 md:pl-20 md:pr-8 md:py-24">
    <h2 id="debrief-title" class="max-w-[40ch] text-headline text-text-primary">
      Then it tells you the truth.
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-5 max-w-[58ch] text-body text-text-primary">
      No gold stars. After every call you get the exact lines you fumbled, the
      slang and idioms you missed, the moment you lost the room, and a survival
      score. It is not encouraging. It is accurate.
    </p>

    <pre class="mt-8 max-w-[52ch] overflow-x-auto rounded-md border border-hairline p-5 font-mono text-caption leading-relaxed text-text-primary md:text-[14px]"><span class="text-text-secondary">SURVIVAL SCORE</span>      <span class="text-failed">42 / 100</span>
You froze at 0:38. He hung up.
<span class="text-text-secondary">MISSED SLANG</span>        "ballpark figure", "no rush"
<span class="text-text-secondary">WEAK MOMENT</span>         "How are you?" (twice)
<span class="text-text-secondary">VERDICT</span>             Survived: <span class="text-failed">NO</span></pre>

    <p class="mt-3 text-caption text-text-secondary">
      Sample debrief. Yours will be worse.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
